title: #153: Swapcast with the Slow News Day Podcast
description:
Happy New Year and thank you for tuning in for another fun festive episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode Sam does a swapcast with Steve Poikonen and Sarah Hall of the Slow News Day podcast! We talk about a wide range of conspiracies. Thank you so much for your love and support. 2018 is going to be an amazing year.
check out the Slow News Day podcast at
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCu4Hp4p1nLy2HYbYiY-NEdA/videos
